<body>
    <header>Stop Child Diabetes</header>
    <section>
        <h2>What is Child Diabetes?</h2>
        <p>Child diabetes, particularly Type 2 diabetes, is a growing concern due to lifestyle factors such as diet and physical inactivity.</p>
        
        <h2>Ways to Prevent Child Diabetes</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Encourage a balanced diet with whole foods, fruits, and vegetables.</li>
            <li>Limit sugary beverages and processed foods.</li>
            <li>Ensure at least 60 minutes of daily physical activity.</li>
            <li>Promote healthy sleep habits.</li>
            <li>Encourage regular medical check-ups.</li>
        </ul>
    </section>
